'''''osto''''' is a noun meaning "stronghold" or "fortress" in [[Quenya]].<ref>{{MR|P4k}}, ''Mandos''</ref> Compare with ''[[ost]]'' in [[Sindarin]].

Examples:
* [[Formenos]] = "Northern Fortress"
* [[Ostoher]] = "Fortress Lord"
